name: Natasha McKinley-Grant
text: I want to say this is by far one of the best customer service experiences we have ever had. Thank you Becca for taking the time and helping us figure out what was wrong when our card malfunctioned. I would recommend this place to all my friends and family and will keep coming back!!!

name: Talia Crawley
text: Great location. Awesome visit. Almost forgot something and both workers came outside and assisted with smiles.

name: Heather McDonald
text: Great service! Several Fresh by the slice or whole pie options. General manager Tony suggested catering for our company functions, which is great for our late nights!  Store was clean and everyone seemed to know their duties. Overall, I will definitely be back!
